{"tid":1102184,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"MOMOLAND 討論區#(13) 忙內Nancy生日粗卡 2019MML繼續大發","createTime":"2019-04-11T13:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T13:41:45.000Z","uid":87223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2485681425ba203dd49cf3c04989dc7bcc6c87e7","tid":1102184,"uid":87223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T13:41:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/25/134505_9edd5bd3ec134c9d651e66bbf243aae7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F25%2F134505_9edd5bd3ec134c9d651e66bbf243aae7.jpg&h=8c559b2e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZQ5Lin.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZQ5Lin.gif&h=5750b4a5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/25/134751_7b4d2f5441c7bc06d5e73f289e235001.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F25%2F134751_7b4d2f5441c7bc06d5e73f289e235001.gif&h=39161227&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MLAw5tW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLAw5tW.gif&h=edb107ff&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/25/134743_0fcce71104a2e5d0cfd7a0f614546baa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F25%2F134743_0fcce71104a2e5d0cfd7a0f614546baa.gif&h=a9bd0efd&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WE2gYZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WE2gYZ.gif&h=bcff8a5a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">MOMOLAND（韓語：모모랜드）</span>，是MLD Entertainment（前稱Dublekick Company）於2016年透過與Mnet合作的練習生競爭節目《SURVIVAL MOMOLAND를 찾아서》選出的女子演唱團體，由10位少女在節目中挑戰不同任務，爭取出道機會，最終選出 慧彬、NANCY、妍雨、娜允、娥仁、JooE、JANE 七名成員。<br />\n<br />\n2017年3月28日，加入曾在《SURVIVAL MOMOLAND를 찾아서》落選， JYP娛樂練習生出身的新成員 DAISY。<br />\n<br />\n2017年4月10日，加入PRODUCE 101出身的新成員 泰河。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">MOMOLAND在打招呼時會說&quot;Get your ticket!&quot;，可知MOMOLAND團名的含意是一座遊樂園。粉絲名為&quot;Merry-go-round / Merry &quot;，意旨MOMOLAND就像旋轉木馬一樣老少咸宜。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">MOMOLAND</span><br />\nYouTube 官方頻道:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/channel/UC62GnXAfqgm8Fcn_i9kiuqw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC62GnXAfqgm8Fcn_i9kiuqw&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzrtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=8f87d1fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/channel/UC62GnXAfqgm8Fcn_i9kiuqw</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">MOMOLAND</span><br />\nTwitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/MMLD_Official\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FMMLD_Official&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzrtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=be130801\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/MMLD_Official</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">MOMOLAND</span><br />\nCafe:<br />\n<a href=\"http://cafe.daum.net/MOMOLAND\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcafe.daum.net%2FMOMOLAND&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzrtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=17355898\" target=\"_blank\">http://cafe.daum.net/MOMOLAND</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">____________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X97Sxn5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX97Sxn5.jpg&h=fcff2059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/25/134644_ce44137ac2eafdedb212f66c1c115862.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F25%2F134644_ce44137ac2eafdedb212f66c1c115862.jpg&h=e34be2b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n____________________________________________</div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">超級重點大事回顧</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2016.11.10 發行出道專輯<br />\n2017.03.28 加入成員Daisy<br />\n2017.04.10 加入成員泰河<br />\n2018.01.11 獲得出道首個一位<br />\n2018.04.23 《BBoom BBoom》突破1億YouTube觀看次數<br />\n2018.06.13 正式於日本出道<br />\n2018.09.26 《BAAM》突破1億YouTube觀看次數<br />\n2019.03.14 MLD Entertainment宣布：Daisy與泰河暫時休息<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">____________________________________________</div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">大型頒獎禮獲獎獎項</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>2017年</ins></strong></span><br />\n名稱：Asia Model Awards<br />\n獎項：<span style=\"color: gold;\">新星獎</span><br />\n<br />\n名稱：第四屆中韓經營大獎<br />\n獎項：<span style=\"color: gold;\">亞洲明日之星獎</span><br />\n<br />\n名稱：第二屆亞洲明星盛典<br />\n獎項：<span style=\"color: gold;\">歌手部門Rising Star賞</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>2018年</ins></strong></span><br />\n名稱：第二屆Soribada最佳音樂大獎<br />\n獎項：<span style=\"color: gold;\">本賞</span><br />\n<br />\n名稱：第三屆亞洲明星盛典<br />\n獎項：<span style=\"color: gold;\">Best Icon獎</span><br />\n<br />\n名稱：第一屆韓國大眾音樂獎<br />\n獎項：<span style=\"color: gold;\">本賞</span><br />\n<br />\n名稱：第一屆MBC Plus X Genie音樂獎<br />\n獎項：<span style=\"color: gold;\">女子最佳舞蹈獎</span><br />\n<br />\n名稱：第十屆甜瓜音樂獎<br />\n獎項：<span style=\"color: gold;\">1theK Performance獎</span><br />\n<br />\n名稱：第二十屆Mnet亞洲音樂大獎<br />\n獎項：<span style=\"color: gold;\">年度發現獎</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>2019年</ins></strong></span><br />\n名稱：第三十三屆金唱片獎<br />\n獎項：<span style=\"color: gold;\">音源本賞</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">____________________________________________</div>"}]}